      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">If your radiators have cold patches at the bottom, your boiler is noisy or your system is slow to heat up, black sludge is almost certainly the cause. Here is everything Liverpool homeowners need to know about power flushing.</p>
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <span><strong>By</strong> Ideal Plumbing Solutions</span>
